snippet.title: LIBBY'S® Famous Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: This is the traditional holiday pumpkin pie. This classic recipe has been on LIBBY'S® Pumpkin labels since 1950. This pie is easy to prepare and even easier to enjoy. Just mix, pour, bake for a delicious homemade tradition.

snippet.title: Lighter Libby's® Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: This lighter pumpkin pie is especially refreshing after a hearty holiday meal.

snippet.title: Crustless LIBBY’S® Famous Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: For some pumpkin pie lovers, the most important part of the pie is the creamy, pumpkin filling. Try this crustless version of Libby's Famous Pumpkin Pie, without the crust, and enjoy more of what you love about this pumpkin holiday tradition. See LIBBY’S® Famous Pumpkin Pie recipe for filling ingredients and mixing directions. Then, see below for baking directions.

snippet.title: LIBBY'S® Easy Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: Want to make a pumpkin pie but do not have spices on hand? Libby's® Easy Pumpkin Pie Mix to the rescue! All you need to bake this treat is a 5 fl.-oz. can of Carnation® Evaporated Milk, 2 large eggs and a 9-inch deep-dish pie shell.

snippet.title: Pumpkin Pie Rice Pudding
snippet.description: Nestlé Kitchens teamed up with Kitchen Play and challenged six food bloggers to deconstruct the pumpkin pie. Check out In Erika’s Kitchen ’s spin on it, Pumpkin Pie Rice Pudding, using Libby’s 100% Pure Pumpkin .

snippet.title: Libby's Homemade Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: For a special treat, try this creamy homemade pumpkin pie recipe. Smooth texture, delicate aroma and incomparable taste will lend a special note to any moment of your day. Serve this delicacy on special occasions and you will make quite an impression on your guests.

snippet.title: La Lechera Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: Cinnamon, nutmeg, ginger and cloves enrich this delicious La Lechera Pumpkin Pie recipe. Top with whipped cream before serving and you'll have a dessert that is perfect for holidays.

snippet.title: Lite 'n Easy Crustless Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: This Lite 'n Easy recipe is creamy and refreshing. Made without a crust, which saves on fat and calories, it's simply mixed and refrigerated until firm.

snippet.title: Sour Cream Orange Pumpkin Pie
snippet.description: This exceptional Sour Cream Orange Pumpkin Pie is spiced with orange peel and topped with a sour cream topping. Perfect for fall entertaining.
